## Technical Writer needed, OWASP 2018


Please see this [job post](link needed) on Upwork and share with your community

Applications to be done at [Upwork](same link)

## OWASP Summit:

“The OWASP Summit 2018 will be a meeting of like-minded professionals focused on solving hard security problems. Participants will join forces in thoroughly prepared working sessions and create actionable solutions to application security challenges.”

